{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-20",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_20_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 20 - If They Hang You",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 1,
  "page_total": 7,
  "page_start_sec": 9.35,
  "page_end_sec": 250.02,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.648,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 9.35,
      "end": 10.62,
      "text": "CHAPTER XX."
    },
    {
      "start": 10.8,
      "end": 12.54,
      "text": "IF THEY HANG YOU"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.75,
      "end": 16.26,
      "text": "For all of five minutes after the outer door",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 16.26,
      "end": 18.68,
      "text": "had closed behind Joel Cairo and Caspar Gutman,"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.22,
      "end": 19.82,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.9,
      "end": 20.52,
      "text": "motionless,"
    },
    {
      "start": 20.68,
      "end": 23.42,
      "text": "stood staring at the knob of the open living-room door."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.1,
      "end": 26.96,
      "text": "His eyes were gloomy under a forehead drawn down.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 27.78,
      "end": 29.62,
      "text": "The clefts at the root of his nose were",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 29.74,
      "end": 30.42,
      "text": "deep and red."
    },
    {
      "start": 31.28,
      "end": 32.56,
      "text": "His lips protruded loosely,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 32.94,
      "end": 33.32,
      "text": "pouting."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.91,
      "end": 35.8,
      "text": "He drew them in to make a hard V"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.04,
      "end": 37.06,
      "text": "and went to the telephone."
    },
    {
      "start": 38.24,
      "end": 39.81,
      "text": "He had not looked at Bridget O'Shaughnessy,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 40.1,
      "end": 41.16,
      "text": "who stood by the table"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.3,
      "end": 42.88,
      "text": "looking with uneasy eyes at him."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.84,
      "end": 45.22,
      "text": "He picked up the telephone,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 45.54,
      "end": 46.9,
      "text": "set it on its shelf again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.44,
      "end": 48.76,
      "text": "and bent to look into the telephone"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.76,
      "end": 51.04,
      "text": "directory hanging from a corner of the shelf."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.48,
      "end": 53.12,
      "text": "He turned the pages rapidly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.46,
      "end": 54.64,
      "text": "found the one he wanted,"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.8,
      "end": 56.08,
      "text": "ran his finger down a column,"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.51,
      "end": 59.26,
      "text": "straightened up and lifted the telephone from the shelf again."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.52,
      "end": 60.84,
      "text": "He called",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 60.84,
      "end": 61.62,
      "text": "a number and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.1,
      "end": 62.56,
      "text": "\"'Hello?"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.74,
      "end": 64.04,
      "text": "Is Sergeant Polehouse there?"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.0,
      "end": 65.58,
      "text": "Will you call him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 65.64,
      "end": 65.9,
      "text": "please?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.12,
      "end": 66.22,
      "text": "This"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.86,
      "end": 68.04,
      "text": "is Samuel Spade.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.18,
      "end": 70.16,
      "text": "He stared into space,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 70.3,
      "end": 70.74,
      "text": "waiting."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.39,
      "end": 72.04,
      "text": "\"'Hello,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 72.08,
      "end": 72.34,
      "text": "Tom?"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.46,
      "end": 73.64,
      "text": "I've got something for you."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.88,
      "end": 74.44,
      "text": "Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 74.62,
      "end": 74.94,
      "text": "plenty."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.8,
      "end": 76.24,
      "text": "Here it is.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 77.216,
      "end": 80.08,
      "text": "Thursby and Jacoby were shot by a kid named Wilmer Cook,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 80.34,
      "end": 81.28,
      "text": "from New York,"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.5,
      "end": 82.16,
      "text": "I think.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.06,
      "end": 84.49,
      "text": "He described the boy minutely.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 85.1,
      "end": 86.32,
      "text": "He's tied up with,"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.48,
      "end": 87.14,
      "text": "working for,"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.34,
      "end": 89.1,
      "text": "a man named Caspar Gutman.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 89.52,
      "end": 90.86,
      "text": "He described Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 91.94,
      "end": 94.86,
      "text": "\"'That fellow Cairo you met here is in with them now also.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 95.74,
      "end": 96.12,
      "text": "\"'Yes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 96.12,
      "end": 96.56,
      "text": "that's it."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.6,
      "end": 99.66,
      "text": "Gutman and the kid have been staying at the Alexandria",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 99.96,
      "end": 100.82,
      "text": "Suite 12C."
    },
    {
      "start": 101.12,
      "end": 103.72,
      "text": "They've just left here and they're blowing town,"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.0,
      "end": 104.64,
      "text": "so you'll"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.64,
      "end": 105.38,
      "text": "have to move quick."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.24,
      "end": 108.0,
      "text": "But I don't think they're expecting a pinch.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 109.12,
      "end": 109.9,
      "text": "There's a girl in it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 109.96,
      "end": 110.12,
      "text": "too,"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.26,
      "end": 111.22,
      "text": "Gutman's daughter.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.9,
      "end": 113.38,
      "text": "He described Ria Gutman.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 114.34,
      "end": 116.16,
      "text": "Watch yourself when you go up against the kid.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 116.34,
      "end": 118.5,
      "text": "He's supposed to be pretty good with the gun."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.68,
      "end": 120.04,
      "text": "That's right,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 120.08,
      "end": 120.28,
      "text": "Tom."
    },
    {
      "start": 120.44,
      "end": 122.56,
      "text": "And I've got some stuff here for you."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.8,
      "end": 125.0,
      "text": "I think I've got the guns he used."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.62,
      "end": 125.76,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.92,
      "end": 126.78,
      "text": "Step on it."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.84,
      "end": 127.84,
      "text": "And luck to you.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 129.024,
      "end": 131.14,
      "text": "Spade slowly replaced receiver on prong,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 131.26,
      "end": 132.32,
      "text": "telephone on shelf."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.56,
      "end": 134.58,
      "text": "He licked his lips and looked down at"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.58,
      "end": 135.04,
      "text": "his hands."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.8,
      "end": 136.72,
      "text": "Their palms were wet.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 137.07,
      "end": 139.14,
      "text": "He filled his deep chest with air."
    },
    {
      "start": 140.0,
      "end": 141.06,
      "text": "His eyes began to glitter",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 141.26,
      "end": 142.44,
      "text": "between straightened lids."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.32,
      "end": 144.66,
      "text": "He turned and took three long,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 144.8,
      "end": 146.36,
      "text": "swift steps into the living-room."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.648,
      "end": 148.46,
      "text": "Bridget O'Shaughnessy,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 148.6,
      "end": 150.34,
      "text": "startled by the suddenness of his approach,"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.7,
      "end": 152.16,
      "text": "let her breath out in a little"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.24,
      "end": 153.18,
      "text": "laughing gasp."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.38,
      "end": 154.6,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.7,
      "end": 155.68,
      "text": "face to face with her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.74,
      "end": 156.8,
      "text": "very close to her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.92,
      "end": 157.38,
      "text": "tall,"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.58,
      "end": 158.94,
      "text": "big-boned and thick-muscled,"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.456,
      "end": 160.22,
      "text": "coldly smiling,"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.48,
      "end": 161.76,
      "text": "heart of jaw and eye,"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.9,
      "end": 162.18,
      "text": "said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.584,
      "end": 164.79,
      "text": "\"'They'll talk when they're pinched.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 164.86,
      "end": 165.7,
      "text": "About us."
    },
    {
      "start": 166.76,
      "end": 167.88,
      "text": "We're sitting on dynamite,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 167.98,
      "end": 168.8,
      "text": "and we've only got"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.94,
      "end": 170.36,
      "text": "minutes to get set for the police."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.56,
      "end": 173.96,
      "text": "I can swing it if I'm sure I know what's what.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 174.94,
      "end": 175.22,
      "text": "Give me",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 175.22,
      "end": 175.66,
      "text": "all of it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.74,
      "end": 176.14,
      "text": "fast."
    },
    {
      "start": 177.408,
      "end": 179.06,
      "text": "Gutman sent you and Cairo to Constantinople?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 180.82,
      "end": 181.84,
      "text": "She started to speak,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 182.04,
      "end": 182.86,
      "text": "hesitated,"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.96,
      "end": 183.72,
      "text": "and bit her lip."
    },
    {
      "start": 184.82,
      "end": 186.04,
      "text": "He put a hand on her shoulder.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 187.232,
      "end": 187.56,
      "text": "\"'Damn you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 187.66,
      "end": 189.0,
      "text": "talk,' he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 189.38,
      "end": 192.02,
      "text": "I'm in this with you and you're not going to gum it."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.22,
      "end": 192.72,
      "text": "Talk."
    },
    {
      "start": 193.9,
      "end": 195.11,
      "text": "He sent you to Constantinople?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 195.98,
      "end": 196.98,
      "text": "Yes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 197.14,
      "end": 198.34,
      "text": "he sent me."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.8,
      "end": 199.7,
      "text": "I met Joe there"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.54,
      "end": 201.66,
      "text": "and—and asked him to help me.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 202.42,
      "end": 203.22,
      "text": "Then we—wait!",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 203.94,
      "end": 206.09,
      "text": "You asked Cairo to help you to get it from Kamidov?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 207.06,
      "end": 207.26,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 208.26,
      "end": 208.992,
      "text": "For Gutman?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 210.12,
      "end": 211.12,
      "text": "She hesitated again,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 211.34,
      "end": 212.58,
      "text": "squirmed under the hard,"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.7,
      "end": 214.02,
      "text": "angry glare of his eyes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.14,
      "end": 214.48,
      "text": "swallowed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.66,
      "end": 215.1,
      "text": "and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.56,
      "end": 216.26,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.4,
      "end": 216.92,
      "text": "not then."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.64,
      "end": 219.16,
      "text": "We thought we would get it for ourselves.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 220.38,
      "end": 220.7,
      "text": "All right.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 221.12,
      "end": 221.22,
      "text": "Then?"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.5,
      "end": 222.6,
      "text": "Oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 222.74,
      "end": 225.94,
      "text": "then I began to be afraid that Joe wouldn't play fair with me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.62,
      "end": 228.34,
      "text": "so—so I asked Floyd Thursby",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 228.34,
      "end": 228.9,
      "text": "to help me."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.98,
      "end": 230.44,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 230.68,
      "end": 231.3,
      "text": "Well?"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.54,
      "end": 231.64,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.88,
      "end": 234.3,
      "text": "we got it and went to Hong Kong.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 235.6,
      "end": 236.16,
      "text": "With Cairo,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 236.3,
      "end": 237.02,
      "text": "or had he been"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.08,
      "end": 237.96,
      "text": "ditched before that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.4,
      "end": 239.36,
      "text": "Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.46,
      "end": 240.76,
      "text": "we left him in Constantinople,"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.2,
      "end": 241.68,
      "text": "in jail,"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.88,
      "end": 243.24,
      "text": "something about a check."
    },
    {
      "start": 244.576,
      "end": 246.14,
      "text": "Something you fixed up to hold him there?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 247.58,
      "end": 249.9,
      "text": "She looked shamefacedly at Spade and whispered,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 249.92,
      "end": 250.02,
      "text": "Yes."
    }
  ]
}